                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070916-78-defend723 t18070916-78-punish410"></join>
               fined One Shilling
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
